@startuml deployment
!include cyber.puml
!include sprites/all.sprite
skinparam linetype ortho

title MedHub - Deployment View (MVP, Docker Compose single host)

node "Client Device\n(desktop / tablet / phone)" as Client #lightgray {
  rectangle "Browser\n(SPA + Cornerstone3D WebGL)" as Browser #lightgray
}

node "Application Host (Docker Compose)" as Host #lightblue {
  rectangle "Reverse Proxy\n(Traefik/nginx)\nTLS 1.2+, HSTS, headers" as Proxy #lightblue
  rectangle "SPA Static Assets\n(nginx)" as StaticSPA #lightblue
  rectangle "Backend API\n(gunicorn + uvicorn, FastAPI)" as ApiC #lightblue
  rectangle "Celery Worker" as WorkerC #lightblue
  database "PostgreSQL 16\n(encrypted volume)" as PGC #lightgray
  queue "Redis\n(sessions + broker)" as RedisC #lightgray
  rectangle "MinIO\n(S3, SSE AES-256)" as MinioC #lightgray
}

node "External Email" as Mail #lightgray {
  rectangle "SMTP Server" as SMTP #lightgray
}

Browser --> Proxy : HTTPS 443 (SR-001, SR-022)
Proxy --> StaticSPA : serve SPA
Proxy --> ApiC : /api -> HTTP (internal)
ApiC --> PGC : SQL (TLS/local)
ApiC --> RedisC : sessions
ApiC --> MinioC : objects (authorized)
ApiC --> RedisC : enqueue tasks
WorkerC --> RedisC : consume tasks
WorkerC --> SMTP : send emails (SR-033, SR-035)
WorkerC --> PGC : SQL

note bottom of Host
  Single-tenant per organization (ADR-0010).
  Secrets injected via env/secret files, never committed.
  Plain HTTP redirected to HTTPS at the proxy.
end note

@enduml
